item.description:
Couch to 5K Graduation!!! 

Great job to our Couch to 5K group and here is our graduation 5K race!!  Wherever you are at, walking, running, jogging or wogging... come join our group for a fun race and an even more fun after race party! 

McGuiggan's Pub 5K road race at McGuiggan's Pub in Whitman, MA

Sunday, June 26th at noon. We can meet there for 11am to register, get bib #'s, and warm up.  

Cost $25 (online has an additional $3 fee)

Online or paper registration available.

http://www.mcguiggans5k.com/index.php

T-shirts to first 700 pre-registered runners. 

Post race block party at McGuiggan's Pub following the race.  (so remember your ID!)  :)

Congrats to all of our graduates!!  I'm SO proud of you all!!
